{
  "stem": "6076.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I felt hot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I felt dizzy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I couldn't-- I felt my head is falling off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My mother looks at me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She says, oh, God in heaven.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "God in heaven, my [INAUDIBLE], you catch typhus.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My child caught the typhus from Zisman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I am going to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "God in heaven, what I'm going to do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're going to kill us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They will come in and burn the whole house with us together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the Germans were afraid for typhus.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They shouldn't-- Catch it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they shouldn't catch it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then this was like a fire.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, Shmulek got up the same symptoms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Ma, he called her, give me a little water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother-- we didn't have a thermometer to-- to-- to see how much temperature.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But feeling the heat, that my-- I couldn't-- the pain in my head, I thought I'd get [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Shmulek was screaming, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Zisman was screaming, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Moishe was the only one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "My mother pushed him out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She touched his forehead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He didn't have temperature.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She said, Moishe, Zisman, go to Aunt Hindi.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] don't stay in the house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Good.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we three of us got very sick, but you cannot hide rumors-- every little thing, neighbors.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right away the ghetto people knew that my cousin Zisman came to the ghetto and brought typhus to us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Right away, I remember clearly that pain, that shame, as being 16-years-old, a girl in that age.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was so alone to myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I felt so devastated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two Jewish policeman walked in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told us we have to be placed where-- in a little-- in a-- it was like in a-- in a place what used to be before the war, a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they made it like a little hospital there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
